extendedInfo.description: Funny Ringtones by Ringhits is a collection of 1,000's of funny and quirky ringtones available for download. These ringtones will make you laugh and surely put a smile on your face, you will simply love them! Funny sounds, tones, text messages, warning calls and alarm sounds will definitely make your mood and make your android device stand out from crowds of unoriginal, default android ringtones!Check the app daily for new ringtones, it updates with fresh sounds every 6 hours!Features:* Thousands of free ringtones* Daily ringtone updates with fresh sounds* Stream ringtones before downloading* Download ringtones to your phone on demand* Search and Browse popular ringtones* Set as ringtone, notification sound or alarm* Assign to specific contact from contact list* Give ringtones ratings and report broken onesApp Includes: Family Guy Soundboards, Stewie Sayings, Quagmire Sayings, Fart Sounds, Prank Calls, Telemarketer Calls, Minion Sounds, Dog ringtones, Siren Ringtones, Alarm Sounds, Anchorman Sounds and Sayings, Stepbrothers Sayings, Startrek Sounds, Star Wars Soundboard, Chapelle, Ricky Boby, Super Mario Tones and Sounds, Herbert, Joker, Will Farrel, Car Horns, Animal Sounds, Baby Sounds, Cat Sounboard, Cartman Sounds, South Park Soundboard and much much more.Compatible with: Ringtone Maker, Ringdroid, Mabilo, RingLert, Zedge, MP3 Ringtone Maker, MP3 Search, Song Downloader and other apps
